What do I like about it? 

-it’s a lightweight, tint like but long wear foundation 
-Dermatologist tested & 100% fragrance-free
-Does not cake or streak and resists water, sweat, and humidity
-Shades available for all Indian Skin Tones

I recommend it 10/10 🌟💯
